Text: Wall Street Journaltoday the Wall Street Journal no longer has individual addresss labels on them Consequently we will distribute them the same way we do the Omaha World Herald There is a sheet at the Front Desk that you need to check off your name when you pick up your copy If you would like Londee to deliver your copy please let us know Thanks for your cooperation Rich Fruge

Building Temperatureare conducting preventative maintenance work on the cooling tower this afternoon It may get a little warm in the building and we are sorry for any inconvenience this may cause Thank you for your patience

Grocery Bags for Recycleare in need of brown paper grocery bags in the kitchen areas to recycle newspaper If you have extra brown paper grocery bags at home please bring them in and put them in the kitchen on your floor Thank you
